    <h3>The 7<sup>th</sup> Convocation of the Eastern Africa Statistical Training Centre(EASTC)</h3>
            <P>The 7<sup>th</sup> Convocation  of the Eastc Africa Statitical Training Centre of the year 2024 continues our culture within academic institutions of gathering together academicians, students, alumni, benefactors, and industry professionals as stskeholders of the  University community.</P>
