                 <h2>Event Details</h2>
                 <p>You are most welcomed to the EASTC 7<SUP>th</SUP> Convocation ceremony</p>
            <p>Which will be conducted <br><b>DATE</b>: Saturday,December 14,2023 <br><b>PLACE</b>: EASTC Campus Found in Changantikeni, DSM<br><b>VENUE</b>: Function Hall  </p>
            <p>The Convocation theme is "<b>Modernizing data ecosystem to accelerate the imprementation of African Continental Free Trade Area<strong>(AfCFTA)</strong>: The role of official statistics and Big Data in the economic transformation and sustainable development of Africa</b> "</p>
               <P>Guest are advised to arrive early to secure parking, complimentary parking is available at the parking block near the program venue</P>
                <p>Guest seating is on a first-come, first-served basis</p>
                <p>Each guest is allocated with a ticket, make sure you register yourself so that you get your ticket</p>
